  "2026-06-04T23:23:02.960Z",codex,"Bugfix (2026-06-04): --body-preview read only item.body, but pm items store prose in description (body usually empty) → silent no-op against real workspaces. Fixed in src/generator.ts to prefer a non-empty body then fall back to item.description; added description? to PmItem. Strictly additive — default output byte-identical (limit 0 early-return). 79 tests pass. Branch fix-changelog-body-preview-description, PR #29."
close_reason: Implemented and tested; default output byte-identical.
